track.name: Left and Right (feat. Jung Kook of BTS)

album.title: Left and Right (feat. Jung Kook of BTS)

wiki.summary: "Left and Right(feat. Jung Kook of BTS)" is a song by Charlie Puth featuring Jungkook of BTS, released through Atlantic Records on (i)June 24, 2022(/i), as the third single from Puth's third studio album, CHARLIE. A catchy, upbeat pop song, the lyrics of "Left and Right" focus on memories of a past love and how consumed by thoughts of that former relationship one can become. An accompanying music video released the same day as the song shows Puth and Jungkook visiting a therapist's office for help with their lovesickness. Read more on Last.fm.
